    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Stance)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 14 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 2 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 13</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This stance has you hunch up, bringing your limbs close and then lashing out like a snake. Unarmed attacks and attacks with Tiny or smaller melee weapons have their attack rolls modified by Dexterity instead of Strength. In addition, you gain a +1 bonus to Defense against attacks of opportunity when you make grapple or disarm attempts.</p>\n\n\n\n",
